# Render Static Site — Redirect & Proxy Rules
# These mirror the routes defined in render.yaml and act as a fallback.
# Order matters: more specific rules must come before the SPA catch-all.

# Proxy /api/* → Spring Boot backend
/api/*  https://droneos-backend.onrender.com/api/:splat  200

# Proxy /ai/*  → Python AI service
/ai/*   https://droneos-ai.onrender.com/ai/:splat  200

# SPA fallback — serve index.html for all other routes so
# React Router handles client-side navigation
/*  /index.html  200
